Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1196,432)}阿莉艾斯
